<plot>A great Party is given by the rich family of Improta. Every kind of intrigue gets around this party. The purpose of every plan is to find a husband or a wife with a quality: wealth. The counts Ornano have invested all they had in Maura, hoping in a good marriage. Mattea gets a fake invitation for her daughter Regina. Nicky Improta has prepared a really great surprise for her mother. Massimo falls in love with Maura Ornano who, according to the family plan, should marry Enrico. The cards are shuffled.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?351361</url></doc>
